#### 2. How to Create a 3-Panel Screen

For a 3-panel screen:

1. Add three `<section>` elements with IDs `pool1`, `pool2`, and `pool3`.
2. Include headers for each pool with titles and buttons to maximize, minimize, or toggle panels.
3. Example:

```html
<section id=\"pool1\" name=\"pool1\" class=\"col-6 panel responsive-height-1\">
  <div id=\"pool1_header\" name=\"pool1_header\" class=\"panel-header\">
    <h2>Pool 1 Title</h2>
