    </button>
  </div>
  <div id=\"list_div\" class=\"panel-content\">
  <section class=\"list\">
  <div class=\"chat-messages\">
    <!-- Content for Pool 1 -->
  </div>
  </section>
  </div>
</section>
```

Repeat similar structures for `pool2` and `pool3`.

#### 3. URL Parameters

- `dark`: Toggles dark mode (`yes` for enabled, `no` for disabled).
- `tab`: Specifies the active tab by its ID.
- `pool1`, `pool2`, `pool3`: Define the state of each pool (`expanded` or `collapsed`).

Example: `?dark=yes&tab=2&pool1=expanded&pool2=collapsed&pool3=expanded`

#### 4. Function: `setDarkMode`

##### Description:
Toggles dark mode and optionally updates user preferences.

##### Syntax:
```javascript
setDarkMode(enable, set_preference=true);
```

- `enable`: `true` to enable dark mode, `false` to disable it.
- `set_preference`: Whether to save the preference (`true` by default).

#### 5. Function: `chooseTab`

##### Description:
Selects a tab and updates the content area.

##### Syntax:
```javascript
chooseTab(tabId, set_preference=true);
```

- `tabId`: The ID of the tab to activate.
- `set_preference`: Whether to save the preference.

#### 6. Function: `closePanel`

##### Description:
Closes (hides) a panel and adjusts the layout.

##### Syntax:
```javascript
closePanel(panelId, set_preference=true);
```

- `panelId`: ID of the panel to close.
- `set_preference`: Whether to save the preference.

#### 7. Function: `openPanel`

##### Description:
Opens (shows) a panel and adjusts the layout.

##### Syntax:
```javascript
openPanel(panelId, set_preference=true);
```

- `panelId`: ID of the panel to open.
- `set_preference`: Whether to save the preference.

#### 8. Function: `togglePanel`

##### Description:
Toggles the visibility of a panel and adjusts the layout.

##### Syntax:
```javascript
togglePanel(panelId, arrowID);
```

- `panelId`: ID of the panel to toggle.
- `arrowID`: ID of the arrow button controlling the panel.

#### 9. Save User Preferences with `setPreference`

##### Example:
```javascript
setPreference(\"dark\", \"yes\"); // Save dark mode preference
setPreference(\"pool1\", \"collapsed\"); // Save panel state
```

#### 10. Load User Preferences with `getPreference`

##### Example:
```javascript
getPreference(\"dark\").then(value => {
  if (value === \"yes\") {
    setDarkMode(true, false);
  }
});
```






